{"tid":2381361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[前車可鑑]巴裔居民即買穆斯林食物　免再受政府供應豬肉類食品","createTime":"2021-01-26T13:36:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T23:47:23.000Z","uid":51271,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0df7ed3fcaf94fb9c5d03796eb2ed66e9c6b00cb","tid":2381361,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T13:36:21.000Z","msg":"Stand News 立場新聞<br />\n <br />\n13 m  &middot;<br />\n【前車可鑑 巴裔居民即買穆斯林食物 免再受政府供應豬肉類食品】<br />\n油麻地碧街 9 至 27 號和東安街 3 號被當局列作「受限區域」，巴基斯坦裔的 Khan 先生得悉住所位於封鎖區之內，立刻到附近的巴基斯坦店舖購買雞蛋、牛奶等食物，「我不知道他們會不會為我們提供（穆斯林）食物」。<br />\n身為穆斯林的 Khan 又指，對於政府早前向油麻地佐敦「受限區域」內的穆斯林派發含有豬肉、豬油的食品感到憤怒，「我的朋友也在裡面，我們很憤怒，因為我們不吃豬肉」。他續稱，香港社區內有不少穆斯林，對於政府沒有考慮穆斯林的需要感到失望。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3845745595511032/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F3845745595511032%2F&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=8051b931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3845745595511032/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/142743166_3845745598844365_2806651961228974103_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=lJJbPS0iNx0AX8HQlRb&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;oh=22b840d9b31028b4661bcdeba4de7fd2&amp;oe=60346E51\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F142743166_3845745598844365_2806651961228974103_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DlJJbPS0iNx0AX8HQlRb%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26oh%3D22b840d9b31028b4661bcdeba4de7fd2%26oe%3D60346E51&h=4ce65ddd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e1aea1a6729903d4b5c004bd3fe5bffcf362d21","tid":2381361,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T13:37:01.000Z","msg":"@UST南亞仔"},{"pid":"74f8edf2d6d75ae3fa940096e71333bd810255fc","